 <div class="panel-pane pane-views-panes pane-donor-stories-panel-pane-2">
  <h2 class="pane-title">
   Donor Stories
  </h2>
  <div class="pane-content">
   <div class="view view-donor-stories view-id-donor_stories view-display-id-panel_pane_2 view-dom-id-e760c13e12407708f1c25d215184fecf">
    <div class="view-content">
     <div class="ucm-view">
      <div class="field-featured-image">
       <a href="/donor-stories/trauma-center-for-21st-century">
        <img alt="It takes all of us: A trauma center for the 21st century" class="vertical-thumbnail" src="https://givetomedicine.uchicago.edu/sites/default/files/styles/vertical_thumbnail/public/images/donor-stories/Trauma_McCormickStory.png?itok=3BaAjMpD" title="It takes all of us: A trauma center for the 21st century" typeof="foaf:Image"/>
       </a>
      </div>
      <span>
       <h5>
        <a href="/donor-stories/trauma-center-for-21st-century">
         It takes all of us: A trauma center for the 21st century
        </a>
       </h5>
      </span>
      <div class="views-field views-field-field-intro-text">
       <div class="field-content">
        Since opening in May 2018, UChicago Medicine's adult Level 1 trauma center saw more than 2,200 trauma patients. The Robert R. McCormick Foundation donated $1 million to support the center's initiatives.
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
     <div class="ucm-view">
      <div class="field-featured-image">
       <a href="/donor-stories/providing-community-support-for-young-women">
        <img alt="Providing a community of support for young women" class="vertical-thumbnail" src="https://givetomedicine.uchicago.edu/sites/default/files/styles/vertical_thumbnail/public/images/donor-stories/HandleyFamily_0.png?itok=1sJDZPr2" title="Providing a community of support for young women" typeof="foaf:Image"/>
       </a>
      </div>
      <span>
       <h5>
        <a href="/donor-stories/providing-community-support-for-young-women">
         Providing a community of support for young women
        </a>
       </h5>
      </span>
      <div class="views-field views-field-field-intro-text">
       <div class="field-content">
        Region’s first pediatric lupus clinic opens at Comer Children’s Hospital thanks to the generosity of the Handley family and Lakeshore Recycling Systems.
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div>
